Place your SAML SP private key and certificate files here.
Files required:
  sp_private.pem   SP private key (never commit)
  sp_cert.pem      SP certificate (can commit, public)

These paths are configured in .env:
  SAML_SP_PRIVATE_KEY_FILE=./saml/sp_private.pem
  SAML_SP_CERT_FILE=./saml/sp_cert.pem

Both files are in .gitignore.
